  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Policy paper on citizens' rights in the event of a no deal Brexit
  </h1>
</div>

  </div>
  

  <div class="column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph ">
    Policy paper outlining the UK Government's action to protect citizens' rights in the event that the UK leaves the EU without a deal.
  </p>

  </div>
</div>

